headline: FICO Partner Awards Demonstrate Power of Advanced Analytics Solutions
summary: HOLLYWOOD, Fla., May 09, 2025--FICO World 25 – At its annual FICO® World conference today, global analytics software leader FICO announced the winners of its second FICO® Partner Awards. These six awards recognize firms that are delivering outstanding value to their business customers using FICO® Platform.
